Subject: [PATCH 10/12] drm/i915/vrr: Use static guardband to support seamless
 LRR switching
Date: Mon, 18 Aug 2025 13:01:26 +0530
Message-ID: <20250818073128.2319762-11-ankit.k.nautiyal@intel.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.45.2
In-Reply-To: <20250818073128.2319762-1-ankit.k.nautiyal@intel.com>
